<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْإنْشِقَاق<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٦:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انْشَقَّتْ <span class="c2">(١)</span> وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَإِذَا الْأَرْضُ مُدَّتْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَأَلْقَتْ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتْ <span class="c2">(٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[الانشقاق: ١ - ٤]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{وَأَذِنَتْ}</span>: <span class="c2">«سَمِعَتْ وَأَطَاعَتْ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{وَأَلْقَتْ}</span> <span class="c2">«أَخْرَجَتْ»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{مَا فِيهَا}</span> <span class="c2">«مِنَ المَوْتَى»</span>،<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{وَتَخَلَّتْ}</span>: <span class="c2">«عَنْهُمْ»</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>